    <studytitle>Placebo controlled,randomised,crossover study of the efficacy of bosentan in the management of patients with Coronary Slow Flow Phenemenon</studytitle>
    <scientifictitle>Study of bosentan in the management of angina in patients with Coronary Slow Flow phenomenon</scientifictitle>
    <utrn />
    <trialacronym>Nil</trialacronym>
